35#include "mech_locl.h"
36
37GSSAPI_LIB_FUNCTION OM_uint32 GSSAPI_LIB_CALL
38gss_delete_name_attribute(OM_uint32 *minor_status,
39 gss_name_t input_name,
40 gss_buffer_t attr)
41{
42 OM_uint32 major_status = GSS_S_UNAVAILABLE;
43 struct _gss_name *name = (struct _gss_name *) input_name;
44 struct _gss_mechanism_name *mn;
45
46 *minor_status = 0;
47
48 if (input_name == GSS_C_NO_NAME)
49 return GSS_S_BAD_NAME;
50
51 HEIM_SLIST_FOREACH(mn, &name->gn_mn, gmn_link) {
52 gssapi_mech_interface m = mn->gmn_mech;
53
54 if (!m->gm_delete_name_attribute)
55 continue;
56
57 major_status = m->gm_delete_name_attribute(minor_status,
58 mn->gmn_name,
59 attr);
60 if (GSS_ERROR(major_status))
61 _gss_mg_error(m, major_status, *minor_status);
62 else
63 break;
64 }
65
66 return major_status;
67}
